<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قَالَ سَالِمٌ:</span> الْمَوْتُ <span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
